



Dr Sir
P[rince] W[illia]m 16th Feby 1775



Cap. Marshall & myself being the persons chosen by our Independent company, to wait on you for the purpose of offering you the command;1 and my not knowing what day he woud call on me, happened to be from home, which prevented my doing myself that pleasure I expected, being quite unprepared for such a journey, the request of the company & likewise of the
[264]
Committee Cap. Marshall will inform you my complets to Mrs Washington self & family concludes me Dr Sir Your Most Obdt

Jas Scott Junr

